,{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"12_1636768103.5455456","card_id":"Q_498203236","target":{"id":498203236,"title":"如何看待上万人数据揭示「童年不幸，更易患病」？情感忽视、家庭暴力等童年不幸经历对人的影响有多大？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/498203236","type":"question","created":1636620945,"answer_count":35,"follower_count":63,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[237,428,3352,5993,20607],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"“幸运的人一生都被童年治愈，不幸的人一生都在治愈童年。”奥地利心理学家阿德勒曾用这句话阐述童年不幸将给人的心理带来永久的伤害。 最近，中山大学公共卫生学院在《美国医学会杂志》子刊上发表的一项研究给这句话加上了新注解。 在对11972名平均年龄为59.85岁的中国居民数据进行统计分析后，研究者们发现，不幸的童年经历（情感忽视、家庭暴力等）可能增加多种慢性疾病及多发病的患病风险，包括血脂异常、慢性肺病、肝病、消化系统疾病等。 该研究还指出，童年不幸与大多数慢性病风险之间存在剂量-反应关系。换言之，一个人所经历的不良童年经历事件越多，长大后这些慢性病发作的风险便越高。 同时，这样的相关性并不会因为参与者年龄、性别、教育水平、年人均家庭支出水平等的不同而受到影响。 上万人数据揭示：童年不幸，更易患病"},"attached_info":"Cj4I1/vk1JS4msJpEAMaCDcyOTkzMTQwIJG1s4wGMAA4P0AMcgk0OTgyMDMyMzZ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"62 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-9aa50ce046fe0adc5a1f8dbfb99d7dbc_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"13_1636768103.5463119","card_id":"Q_342445699","target":{"id":342445699,"title":"你有哪些住宿必备好吃不贵的零食？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/342445699","type":"question","created":1566616780,"answer_count":643,"follower_count":4316,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[304,568],"comment_count":8,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8I1/vk1JS4msJpEAMaCDM4Mzc2MTg3IMzZgusFMAg43CFADXIJMzQyNDQ1Njk5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"62 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-71e1f85cdc7215c91a4847469da684a8_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_li